OOC: Jason, last time I posted fire with Triggerhappy and Blowpipe at Astro=
 Train, you never replied, or I might've missed it.  So, read the last part=
 with Triggerhappy and Blowpipe and post damage.

::Composer/Symphony/Trigg=
erhappy::

         Composer grinned.

         "Yes!  We should tell Zardu=
s what we've accomplished," He said.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~=
~~~~~
        Symphony walked out of the CR Chamber he was in.  Now he was =
fully healed after being in there for quite a while.  But he could still he=
ar fire, so he went outside to help his comrades.  He ran out, and saw Prow=
l and Iron Raptor on the gestalt Menasor, and Firearm being badly beaten up=
 by Squawktalk and Beastbox.  Symphony thought for a moment, then he figure=
d Prowl and Iron Raptor could handle Menasor, after all, Prowl had a wicked=
 body and all.  So Symphony whipped out his machine gun at started firing 2=
5 rapid shots at Sqawktalk in hopes to send him down out of the air.
~~~~~~=
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
          Triggerhappy fired 2 shots =
from each photon cannon at Astro Train.  His cockpit window was slightly op=
en, and in it was Blowpipe.  Blowpipe fired 2 lasers out at Astro Train.
